Qgj.jpg&h=e0cdff0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n揮著紅旗打紅旗，<br />\n要改變萌塞思想，<br />\n膠化propaganda就係上策。<br />\n順著佢哋嘅思路，<br />\n只講佢哋關心嘅嘢。<br />\n<br />\n由保民生抗修例大聯盟作為起點，<br />\n呢項運動，必須進化。<br />\n<br />\n長遠嚟講，我哋唔單止要抗修例，<br />\n更加要話俾廢中廢老知道，<br />\n明日大嶼、醫管局私隱醜聞、<br />\n係會確切影響佢哋嘅生活，<br />\n從而改變佢哋嘅思想，<br />\n轉化佢哋嘅立場取態。<br />\n<br />\n大聯盟配合真建制派，<br />\n就如民X聯配李思嫣一樣，相輔相成。<br />\n直至推到有人真係出錢參選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">下一屆議會，由我哋連登仔女帶頭改變</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T10:41:21.000Z","msg":"果日我先見到有囡囡拎住一疊傳單入黎買野飲<br />\n好正好索<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n已登記做選民"},{"pid":"6aade86fc1f8c162fdb83a0af48eea4ae496988a","tid":1239180,"uid":187050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T11:58:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1a9b1f29167559fa3d748b5009bb9f88c897ec4a","tid":1239180,"uid":126054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T12:00:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"913b2e4acb46cdb8b7a974a514b9d8bd7b8d53c0","tid":1239180,"uid":43983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T13:52:58.000Z","msg":"需要幫手印嗎？<br />\n呢排公司全力比我印傳單派比街坊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6689796ede6832813815f92b264c605a12e3480","tid":1239180,"uid":128369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T14:49:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1db6fda74c418cbd35e6dd13aedeca87f9095a0c","tid":1239180,"uid":29895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T14:54:06.000Z","msg":"推"}]}